title: Show HN: Use QR code to send data to phone easily - Easytophone.com
text:
Hello,

I created a web site where you can send text, calendar events and file to your phone easily.

Once the data is submitted, it shows a QR code where you can scan it with your phone. Tapping on the QR code will direct you to easytophone.com and the data download will start.

In terms of technology there is not much new or exciting. But maybe it will be useful for you?

I plan to show some ads in the future. Maybe have a paid option for larger files. Maybe API service??

Do you think there is a potential for some meaningful usage?

Do you see anything that can be improved?

This should work fine on iPhone. I haven't tested it on Android yet.

Any input is welcome!! Thank you!

Luca Marudot
